# Prototype Development Plan

## Prototype Milestones

| Prototype milestone | What must be completed | Deadline | Evidence |
|--------------------|------------------------|-----------|-----------|
| Milestone 1 | Create first simple version of the game/prototype | End of Week 2 | Screenshots, links, and files |
| Milestone 2 | Add feedback, rewards, or learning explanation | Start of Week 3 | Updated screenshots and files |
| Milestone 3 | Test with group members and collect feedback | Mid Week 3 | Testing notes |
| Milestone 4 | Prepare presentation evidence | End of Week 3 | Slides and prototype demo |

